data.description: Built in 2021 on a 5+ acre lot in Samworth Loop, only 20 minutes to downtown Georgetown or Myrtle Beach, this beautiful 3 BR, 2.5 bath home with attached 2 car garage is a wonderfully tranquil retreat.  Gourmet kitchen, office of owners' suite with great views of property, gas fireplace between living/dining areas, man cave off kitchen/dining rooms, sitting area on 2nd floor for guests (or gaming area for kids), top floor writing nook/office area with views of property.  And lots of great outdoor space with covered front porch and back porch complete with retractable awning, under house space, not to mention the more than 5 acres with pond!  Call for a showing before it's too late!
